@node "ReKeyIt History" "ReKeyIt History"
@prev "History"
 -------------
 Revision V1.3
 -------------

     Ę Added locale support.

 -------------
 Revision V1.2
 -------------

     Ę Sometimes ReKeyIt would fail to change the menus and
       an error would not be reported.  Fixed Ę I Hope :-)

     Ę Added retry to error requester if menus could not by found

     Ę Changed method of checking for errors, should be more
       accurate now.

 -------------
 Revision V1.1
 -------------

     Ę You can now specify ReKeyIt as a default tool in a the
       icon of a prefs file, and just double click on the prefs
       file to set the menus.

     Ę Old shortcuts still worked, even though they were
       not being displayed in the menus. (fixed)

     Ę Now menu names in config are case insensitive.

 -------------
 Revision V1.0
 -------------

       --- Initial release ---
@endnode

@node "MenuPrefs (MUI) History" "MenuPrefs (MUI) History"
@prev "History"
 -------------
 Revision V1.2
 -------------

     Ę Added missing version string.

     Ę If create icons was selected and an error occured while saving, the
       icon would be created anyway  (fixed)

     Ę String gadget was not disabled if nothing in the listview
       was selected (fixed)

     Ę Added locale support

 -------------
 Revision V1.1
 -------------

     Ę Moved 'Last Saved' to menus

     Ę Keyboard can be used to control listview.

 -------------
 Revision V1.0
 -------------
